 of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done to improve security, stability, and performance. \n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 04 Nov 2016 01:18:00 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/xd9cv3gc9m1c\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/xd9cv3gc9m1c\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Grid Hardware Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1654:\"\n<p><small>Oct 31, 21:18 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - The scheduled maintenance has been completed.</p><p><small>Oct 31, 21:01 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Oct 28, 13:56 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing a scheduled system maintenance on Monday, October 31st 2016 to our Grid hosting service. Here are the important details:\n<br />\n<br /><b>Who is affected?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect customers on the following servers:\n<br />\n<br />(gs) Grid-Service, Cluster 9, herd 01.\n<br />\n<br />You may verify whether or not your services are being impacted by this issue by locating your Cluster and Storage Segment in your Server Guide. For more information on how to locate your Server Guide in the AccountCenter, please reference the following (mt) Community article.\n<br />\n<br />Server Guide\n<br />https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/server-guide\n<br />\n<br /><b>When will this maintenance happen?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will occur between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM PT, , Monday, October 31st 2016.\n<br />\n<br /><b>What is changing?</b>\n<br />\n<br />(mt) Engineers are installing software updates on the operating system. \n<br />\n<br /><b>Why is this maintenance happening?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done as preventative maintenance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />• Inability to access websites on Herd 01 Cluster 9 during reboot.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 31 Oct 2016 21:18:51 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/q74h35zqfh94\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/q74h35zqfh94\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Network Hardware Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1435:\"\n<p><small>Oct 28, 00:59 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - At this time, our Admins have confirmed that the maintenance has been completed. Access to the servers and websites should be restored. If you are still having issues, please contact support.</p><p><small>Oct 27, 21:10 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Oct 27, 09:20 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing scheduled system maintenance on Thursday, October 27, 2016 to our network infrastructure. Here are the important details: \n<br />\n<br />Who is affected? \n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect customers on our DV servers as well as email on our Grid Shared servers. \n<br />\n<br />When will this maintenance happen? \n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will occur between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM PT, Thursday, October 27, 2016. \n<br />\n<br />What is changing? \n<br />\n<br />(mt) Engineers will be swapping out network equipment with new and improved hardware to avoid issues moving forward.\n<br />\n<br />Why is this maintenance happening? \n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done as preventative maintenance. \n<br />\n<br />Symptoms: \n<br />• Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP on DV. \n<br />• Inability to access email on Grid.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 00:59:33 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s