 equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done as preventative maintenance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP on DV.\n<br />•  Inability to access email on Grid.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 27 Oct 2016 22:39:45 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/yb8lcfjc8bff\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/yb8lcfjc8bff\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Account Center Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1355:\"\n<p><small>Oct 27, 21:11 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - The scheduled maintenance has been completed.</p><p><small>Oct 27, 21:00 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Oct 27, 09:28 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing scheduled system maintenance on Thursday, October 27th, 2016 to our Account Center. Here are the important details:\n<br />\n<br /><b>Who is affected?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect the Account Center.\n<b